data.description: This is unique and beautiful, recently renovated home/office located in the heart of Lonoke. The property has 4-bedrooms and 3-full bathrooms featuring approximately 2,905 square feet of living space, with an additional 619 square feet of finished bonus space. A sunlit entry opens into spacious living, office/bedroom, and dining areas. Bedrooms, workspace, kitchen, and bathrooms extend though the first level, with a gorgeous sunroom upstairs. The home was thoroughly renovated with updates including new plumbing, electric, roof, flooring, fixtures, kitchen, and bathrooms. The property sits on a spacious lot and is within walking distance to downtown. The home has been used as an office in the past and would also make a perfect professional office. A VA loan assumption at below market rate of 3.625% is possible for residential use at an increased price. Property sold As-Is.
